- VSCode Version: 0.10.11
- OS Version: OSX 10.10.5

Steps to Reproduce:
- Create a simple plugin doing nothing but updating the same line decoration in a interval:

``` javascript
var i = 0;
var decType = window.createTextEditorDecorationType({});

setInterval(() => {
  var decoration = {
    range: new vscode.Range(0, 0, 0, 1000),
    hoverMessage: 'test' + (++i)
  };
  window.activeTextEditor.setDecorations(decType, [decoration]);
}, 200);
```
- Observe the decoration hover message not being changed, even when the line content is changing (only deleting the line seems to update the message):

